In the words of @AuroraJames. NARS sat down with the Creative Director of @BrotherVellies to learn how she founded @15PercentPledge in a matter of days.
 
Captured during a #MetGala beauty test with Global Artistry Director @U.z.o.
 
NARS is proud to donate to #FifteenPercentPledge as part of Beauty of Change, our cause platform dedicated to empowering and educating for a bold-faced future. To learn how you can support the Fifteen Percent Pledge’s fight for economic equality and prosperity, head to our Stories.
 
Video by @Dapper.Studios

node.text:
@AuroraJames, founder of @BrotherVellies and @15PercentPledge, wears a full face of NARS for #MetInAmerica. Global Artistry Director @U.z.o on the inspiration: 
 
“The beauty look combines elements of Aurora’s personal style with a 1960’s aesthetic, à la Jackie O—a nod to classic American beauty. Timeless black winged liner defines the eyes against a soft natural backdrop of luminous skin and a rosy lip.”
 
Get The Look: 
Pure Radiant Tinted Moisturizer
Soft Matte Complete Concealer
Climax Liquid Eyeliner
Orgasm Afterglow Lip Balm
#regram #MetGala
